news.title: Nashik: EV charging stations must for all new buildings with 25+ flats
news.para: NMC commissioner Kailas Jadhav said he has already passed an order and directed the town planning department to not approve building plan proposals if they do not have provisions for EV charging stations.

news.title: DHFL case: Yes Bank's former business head gets bail
news.para: ​​Anand's bail plea was allowed by special judge for CBI cases S U Wadgaonkar. The detailed order was not available yet. The bank's co-founder Rana Kapoor and his family are co-accused in the case.

news.title: Delhi court takes cognisance of charge sheet against Unitech promoters
news.para: "Considering the material available on record, I take cognisance for the commission of offence punishable under section 3 and 4 (money laundering) of Prevention of Money Laundering Act (PMLA). Let accused persons be summoned for next date of hearing," the judge said.

news.title: Essar Steel Metal Trading buys luxury duplex in Mumbai's Worli for Rs 42 crore
news.para: The deal values the luxury pad at more than Rs 1.44 lakh per sq ft, making it one of the costliest apartment transactions in the country. The duplex spread over 3,638 sq ft carpet area is on the 21st and 22nd floor of the sea-facing building on Dr. Annie Besant Road.

news.title: Debenture holders oppose Adani Realty's bid for Radius Estates
news.para: ICICI Pru AMC and Beacon Trusteeship, who hold debentures of Radius, have approached NCLT to stop voting on Adani’s bid.

news.title: Allianz invests $871 million in Heimstaden's Sweden property portfolio
news.para: The agreement will form a joint venture on the 30.4 billion Swedish crown portfolio, which includes 3,377 homes in Malmo and 5,932 homes in Stockholm, the asset manager said in a statement.

news.title: Prestige Group signs civil contract worth Rs 1,560 crore with Larsen & Toubro
news.para: The scope of work involves construction of towers and villas, comprising of 6,768 apartments over 39 towers. The project is scheduled to be completed in 42 months

news.title: CenturyPly to set up plant in Andhra Pradesh
news.para: Andhra Pradesh Chief Minister YS Jagan Mohan Reddy on Thursday laid foundation stone for the proposed plant, a release from the wood panel maker said.

news.title: DDA & YEIDA launch housing scheme, 18,335 flats & 416 plots on offer
news.para: DDA said that flats offered under this scheme are those which remain unsold in previous housing schemes of DDA.

news.title: Firozabad: Rs 1.92 crore 'scam' in PMAY, FIR registered
news.para: According to the FIR, the officer had transferred Rs 1.92 crore into the bank accounts of 221 ineligible applicants under the PM housing scheme in 2019.

news.title: Telangana government green signal to auction Kokapet land
news.para: It maybe recollected the government sold Kokapet lands through e-auctioning in July this year which garnered huge response as eight plots over 48.27 acre were offered for a minimum upset price of Rs 25 crore per acre.

news.title: South Delhi civic body conducts tax survey of government properties
news.para: SDMC has set a target of collecting Rs 1,200 crore as property tax, and till now, Rs 762.9 crore has already been collected by the corporation, out of which 4,00,553 were residential properties and the remaining were commercial properties.

news.title: Ahmedabad civic body seals 20 commercial units without building use permission
news.para: The town planning and estate department teams also demolished 28,685 sq feet of illegal construction of 18 commercial properties located in various areas of the city.

news.title: Indiabulls Real Estate approves plan to raise up to Rs 1,500 crore
news.para: The board of directors of the company has approved raising of funds, aggregating upto Rs 1,500 crore through one or more Qualified Institutions Placement in one or more tranches, Indiabulls Real Estate said in the regulatory filing.

news.title: Greater Noida: Soon, you can rate upkeep in your society
news.para: Officials said the rating of a particular society would be done on the feedback received from its residents across 10 parameters such as sanitation, maintenance of lift, electric supply and common areas.
